From peter.hickey at gmail.com  Mon Feb  6 16:22:41 2017
From: peter.hickey at gmail.com (Peter Hickey)
Date: Mon, 6 Feb 2017 10:22:41 -0500
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Registering native routines with Rcpp
Message-ID: <CAB6GOe6qQ9F0E5aJkOKwE_0WLb1veFmGGtgRFNBLmm=R4LRi8Q@mail.gmail.com>

FWIW I've had some success registering Rcpp-based native routines
using Kmisc:::registerFunctions() by Kevin Ushey
(https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/Kmisc/index.html). Note this
is a non-exported function and from memory it required a little bit of
post-processing, but it got me most of the way there.

Cheers,
Pete


